re slippage.  This condition can vary by terrain type.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="?$rBk?gLLoAK#p5j[.5,"><field name="NUM">20</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="bW*E;th^e~u(?Ug5.YgZ"><field name="VAR" id="Pn4_q~v_/TkrLShW@pU.">accel_rate</field><comment pinned="false" h="109" w="459">This variable controls the rate of the acceleration ramp-- how long the bot takes to get from zero to max. In initial testing 1 worked well, 2 produced tire slippage.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="-)Cx|m#tYX]8@d6~:%hC"><field name="NUM">1</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="0M3_w?hH/-Bm|SOM!UGl"><field name="VAR" id="`=ApUrD}(0qDd^Yp4(rh">max_normal_speed</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="X.6iYu0?yDF9cMA$3JTJ"><field name="NUM">99</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="?}yvTC?tSYSA^)`^V[p_"><field name="VAR" id="Bdy2d{-@DtkKH1)=c_,-">max_turbo_speed</field><comment pinned="false" h="119" w="369">This value will determine the maximum speed to which the bot will accelerate before topping out. Valid range is 0 to 100.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="GU1=!4HScC[p3mbjDql|"><field name="NUM">99</field></shadow></value><next><block type="quest_Note_4_quest_Show_String_For_Note_Small_Func" id="Q3YCqtj-{KcB0a5C?pf?"><value name="textStrIn"><shadow type="text" id="1Zm3WTt|5Bz8XXp;Cd$r"><field name="TEXT">Tap-to-turn variables</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id=":5#_3K1kz!nlQGmvy|NF"><field name="VAR" id="{9/P79Oy?=geDGf!_*AJ">tap_left_turn_bias</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="A$dQq8uU?#ONT%]